@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: User Login

actor User
participant "SIMKEL" as System
database "Database" as DB

User -> System: Masukkan Username & Password
activate System

System -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ?
activate DB
DB --> System: User data
deactivate DB

alt Kredensial Valid
    System --> User: Login Berhasil, Tampilkan Dashboard
else Kredensial Tidak Valid
    System --> User: Login Gagal, Tampilkan Pesan Error
end

deactivate System

@enduml
